# Keep the build context small for services built from the repo root
# (context: ..). None of these are needed by any Dockerfile.
.git
vendor
**/node_modules
**/target
**/__pycache__
**/.next
**/out
**/*.class
**/.pytest_cache
infra/certs/*.key
# CDK build output — must be excluded, otherwise repo-root image builds (gateway,
# auth) recursively copy infra/cdk/cdk.out into themselves.
**/cdk.out
# Build artifacts (e.g. apps/desktop-app/dist Electron output) — not needed by any image.
**/dist
